{"tid":2047753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美聯社：世衛官員私下不滿中國提供疫情資訊不足","createTime":"2020-06-02T10:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T12:01:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d46a61f224b29f503650f17684b2356d5ca6a6a4","tid":2047753,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"世衛多次公開讚揚中國在疫情防控工作，但美聯社報道，世衛官員私下對中國提供的資訊不足感到不滿，公開讚揚中國是為了獲取更多資訊。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社取得錄音，發現世衛官員在1月初的會議，曾經抱怨中國分享疫情資訊不足，難以評估病毒能夠有效人傳人的程度，以及對世界構成的風險。世衛駐華代表亦在另一場會議中說，中國政府直到央視公布前15分鐘，才將疫情資訊提供給世衛。<br />\n<br />\n目前在世衛負責領導抗疫工作的美國流行病學家，在一次內部會議上說，他們從中國獲得的資訊很少，無法做適當的應變計劃。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社認為，這些事件顯示，中國明顯延誤通報疫情，而世衛官員對未能取得抗疫所需資訊，感到挫折。"},{"pid":"290ce6de30b0d6c46ef8e64e0d8a35e043416251","tid":2047753,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1297591&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5266cc9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297591</a>"},{"pid":"ade653a9d8165c5b0bbd4ca159321b8dceaa48dc","tid":2047753,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1784088f77ddd376fad3b9d502092d655b63add2","tid":2047753,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:16:59.000Z","msg":"今次AP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe8b74d351543c645630ef7e50b8740d1985bb9","tid":2047753,"uid":238415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"私下不滿 